<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><style>body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }</style></head>
<body>
  <h2>Action Required: Hackathon Needs Changes</h2>
  <p>Hello <%= organizerName %>,</p>
  <p>We reviewed your hackathon <strong><%= title %></strong>, but it currently cannot be verified for the following reason:</p>
  <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #ccc; padding-left: 10px; color: #555;">
    <%= rejectionReason %>
  </blockquote>
  <p>Your hackathon has been reverted to Draft status. Please make the necessary adjustments in your organizer dashboard and re-publish for verification.</p>
  <p>Best,<br>FAIRJUDGE Team</p>
</body>
</html>
